#inline#mFMb_DS_GetIdleTimer( { idleMode } )/*	What it does:	It gets the number of seconds that the myFMbutler DoScript plug-in wil wait before going into the next idle processing for the given idle mode.		Required parameters:	none. It returns the timer for semiSafeIdle when no parameter is passed to the function.		Optional parameters:		idleMode	"safeIlde", "semiSafeIdle" of "unSafeIdle"		returns:	the number of seconds FileMaker will wait in its idle loops		could return myFMbutler error 9 / Evaluation Error 1224		notes:	the smaller this number, the more frequent the DoScript plug-in will evaluate the trigger.		It *could* slow you down...*/